text.section:
While serving on the commission, a member shall not:
Serve as a fundraiser for a slate of candidates for Governor and Lieutenant Governor, or candidate for Attorney General, Auditor of Public Accounts, or the General Assembly;
Contribute to a slate of candidates for Governor and Lieutenant Governor, or candidate for Attorney General, Auditor of Public Accounts, or the General Assembly;
Serve as an officer in a political party; or
Participate in the management or conduct of the political campaign of a candidate.
